				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I'm seeing a pattern ;)<BR>
<BR>
Wood-Elf/Halfing Druid - No melee, suicide<BR>
<BR>
Half-Elf/Human Druid - Some melee is ok, just don't tank<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Now I don't claim to be the world's greatest damage sponge, but I can certainly help every once and awhile, especially if I'm not targetted by the melee.  I can even fake tanking if I'm partnered with a cleric.  I evade often enough (and have enough of a channeling skill) to cast during combat as well, etc etc etc...<BR>
<BR>
I wouldn't suggest you go off and tank in the planes, or any such thing, but it is handy to not have to run like a headless chicken everytime a baddy looks at you the wrong way ;)
